{"tid":845842,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"剝過智慧齒既請入","createTime":"2018-10-03T03:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T12:29:29.000Z","uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"da670bda8f67cc59e846b1faac0ad7d9f87263b1","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"最近飲凍水同食朱古力都會牙痛，於是去睇睇牙醫。<br />\n睇完之後牙醫話我4隻智慧齒都蛀左，建議我剝哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲報價4000蚊剝一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （我係恒健睇）<br />\n想問有冇剝過智慧齒既巴絲可以分享下邊度剝牙手勢好而且又冇咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49d515d93685ae0d4f698a0af0b432969565761","tid":845842,"uid":193613,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"屌 你放張x光上黎 <br />\n你四隻都要開刀？"},{"pid":"d3f01bdef0e7e17b4267e9ee684f798d208678ab","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b49d515d93685ae0d4f698a0af0b432969565761","tid":845842,"uid":193613,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"屌 你放張x光上黎 <br />\n你四隻都要開刀？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/120708_439d46b0a6ba8a742db443cff7005047.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F120708_439d46b0a6ba8a742db443cff7005047.png&h=43ed5a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生話4隻都蛀左，建議我剝哂佢"},{"pid":"40beae9899ea7591697950e81d0ac1b8c0392ad5","tid":845842,"uid":198616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3f01bdef0e7e17b4267e9ee684f798d208678ab","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b49d515d93685ae0d4f698a0af0