},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"一陣會去旺角，順便問一問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"如果開始痛 我建議盡快剝<br />\n因為可能突然痛得好勁<br />\n食藥都止唔到痛<br />\n我試過去旅行果陣痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e838cafcea39b3dd8d651209fa34e5b8baafeba","tid":845842,"uid":198616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21a5d83336ee3ec9548076ec48c4f8b2da0e1744","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd3744e9abe485b6a9b289f3877e3b5dbfcf7a6","tid":845842,"uid":198616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f2e9c471b95403a9745d06638a8033f55560f9","tid":845842,"uid":198616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:17:33.000Z","msg":"喂唔一定嫁喎，要視乎佢點做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"你想知detail 我再講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便問下你全身麻醉之後有冇副作用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"我果陣4隻全横生，冇痛，但見後生咪快趣剝，家人都有呢個問題但太老放棄剝，<br />\n咁就去菲臘排期，成個過程搞幾耐冇印象。之後入瑪麗醫院做"},{"pid":"89915c2eb0c9ab615436e3394c84ca9c56099637","tid":845842,"uid":32265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"旺角彌敦道610號荷李活商業中心2103室<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上次單剝一隻 $3200有找<br />\n之後要開刀剝一隻 $5200有找 <br />\n價錢計埋藥 x-ray 麻醉<br />\n比你參考下 始終唔同牙醫睇 唔同價錢 <br />\n總結 好撚爽手 而且得少少痛 我即日可以食到飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3165691aad1224c9625df85754bac1781db81653","tid":845842,"uid":87925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1bd705361b888a531965e2f0e5d12f521b52e9","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e283220d78f6b904dcfca134d7564b1cc219c1fe","tid":845842,"uid":10139,"like":0,"dis