=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全身麻醉係令你冇知覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"俾你咁講我霎時唔肯定，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我夜做，半夜唔比你落床，驚你麻醉冇力，<br />\n但其實第2日中午左右己放你走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"唔係麻醉冇力<br />\n係費事你痛到訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f425d2cd9fa3e481837003472ca332188195e462","tid":845842,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"黎緊11月會剝 兩隻下面都打橫生 DKLM <br />\n智障齒 分開兩次 驚一次兩邊開刀剝晒 會成個星期食唔到野"},{"pid":"ededef6e8617a6b06f4ab62e1ddbf033ba181074","tid":845842,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"3000 一隻"},{"pid":"5437d66f8219bbc1a892d66b17f47a73d2b1291a","tid":845842,"uid":47679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"之前剝過一隻無蛀800幾咋wo  30秒唔洗手勢幾好係上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb35d95c657ea45e28aeadb9a26133330cd69b6","tid":845842,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:48:55.000Z","msg":"我上面兩隻打直正常生，但蛀左，每隻1700，打完麻醉等左十分鐘，之後醫生用一分鐘就搞掂一隻，塞舊棉花就走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我兩隻係一個月內蛀哂，搞到分左兩次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ec89e20591d39ffbf0f4a71158eebf86ff0898","tid":845842,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"剝2隻先4200咋喎 隔下價先好喎"},{"pid":"d125ab1822386d429df62d838309d316748ede03","tid":845842,"uid":100924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"今年剝2隻 鄧醫生<br />\n下面開刀 全包 3500<br />\n上面有蛀900 加100藥(可以唔要)<br />\n<br />\n樓主你下面2隻一定要快啲剝 <br />\n如果唔係前面隻牙有機會頂爛同蛀 <br />\n到時前面嗰隻要杜牙根仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8414a8526df5f62400237ccc7cf1f2ea2dfe76e","tid":845842,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"同你一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n恒健報價 ＄8000 兩隻（手術科牙醫）<br />\n都係話要做 4隻<br />\n<br />\n之後我出去搵間開左幾十年嘅<br />\n由個後生d 牙醫做（未拎到手術科）<br />\n最後＄6500 兩隻（一隻要開刀）"},{"pid":"c2959584fe7db4985deb09a75fbb98d06b5f9675","tid":845842,"uid":100924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94c17e018441733832e7e75a59e5846b7617a4be","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"暫時決定下個禮拜去菲力到排隊預約，希望佢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔收就畢業做野儲錢再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"排到自然好 唔收怕隻牙唔等到你grad完做野再儲錢剝<br />\n到時痛到你借財仔都剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6de07728a147a28398a6f3cf04af5a675bc4dc","tid":845842,"uid":106673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打 知道如果剝完再箍牙有冇平啲 定全部分開計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c1b905e1817e4e089eb103efdb23374c4b05f8","tid":845842,"uid":193827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"下星期去菲臘剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af79a5d736596d5714c38304d9492981e6adccb5","tid":845842,"uid":28485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da670bda8f67cc59e846b1faac0ad7d9f87263b1","tid":845842,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"最近飲凍水同食朱古力都會牙痛，於是去睇睇牙醫。<br />\n睇完之後牙醫話我4隻智慧齒都蛀左，建議我剝哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲報價4000蚊剝一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （我係恒健睇）<br />\n想問有冇剝過智慧齒既巴絲可以分享下邊度剝牙手勢好而且又冇咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"同你一樣食朱古力就成排大牙酸痛<br />\n但醫生話我敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}